---
const painPoints = [
  {
    title: "Leads slipping through the cracks",
    text: "You got 50 leads last month. How many heard from you in the first 2 minutes? Manual follow-up doesn't scale and the best prospects move on while you're still in your inbox.",
    link: "/projects/inbound-ai-sdr",
    category: "Lead-Gen"
  },
  {
    title: "Operations eating your day",
    text: "Sorting resumés, onboarding clients, responding to reviews, chasing paperwork, the admin work that runs in the background of every service business shouldn't require a human.",
    link: "/projects/onboarding-workflow",
    category: "Operations"
  },
  {
    title: "Your processes don't fit a template",
    text: "Route planning, inventory tracking, custom workflows, you've thought \"there has to be a better way\" more than once. If you can describe the process, we can probably automate it.",
    link: "/projects",
    category: "Custom"
  }
];
---

<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="tracker-label" data-animate="fade-up">
        <span class="num">03</span> SOUND FAMILIAR
      </span>
      <h2 data-animate="fade-up">If you've thought any of these, we should talk.</h2>
      <p data-animate="fade-up">
        These are the problems we solve every day for service businesses already doing real revenue.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pain-grid" data-animate-stagger>
      {painPoints.map((pain) => (
        <a href={pain.link} class="pain-card" data-track="problem_card_click" data-track-label={pain.title}>
          <span class="pain-category">{pain.category}</span>
          <h3 class="pain-title">{pain.title}</h3>
          <p class="pain-body">{pain.text}</p>
          <span class="pain-link">See the fix <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="bottom-stat" data-animate="fade-up">
      <p>You're great at what you do. But between marketing and operations, the busywork keeps piling up. <strong>It doesn't have to.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
    background: var(--bg-surface-alt);
  }

  .problem-header {
    max-width: var(--max-narrow);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .problem-header h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .problem-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lead);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: var(--max-content);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pain-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pain-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .pain-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition:
      transform var(--dur-base) var(--ease-out-expo),
      border-color var(--dur-base) var(--ease-out-expo),
      box-shadow var(--dur-base) var(--ease-out-expo);
    min-height: 280px;
  }

  .pain-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--orange);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    color: inherit;
  }

  .pain-card:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .pain-category {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .pain-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pain-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .pain-link {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out-expo), color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .bottom-stat {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: var(--max-content);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bottom-stat p {
    font-size: var(--text-lead);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .bottom-stat strong {
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bottom-stat {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
